{"title":"【DSA】Python线性数据结构","uid":"ccd272a242e0bb6cfd7d7d1be2f89c14","slug":"Python基本数据结构","date":"2022-12-19T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-19T13:40:19.463Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Python基本数据结构.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/python/DSA/1/cover.jpg","content":"<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>本篇的目标是使用Python实现常用的线性数据结构并使用，包括：栈、队列、双端队列、链表等。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"队列\"><a href=\"#队列\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"队列\"></a>队列</h1><p>队列的的排序原则是先进先出（FIFO）。其中添加操作发生在队列的尾部，移除操作发生在队列的头部。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/python/DSA/1/image-20221219175729656.png\" alt=\"image-20221219175729656\"></p>\n<p>先进先出的使用是很普遍的，如生活中的排队，操作系统中的阻塞队列、就绪队列，网络中的请求队列等，都使用到了队列这一模型。</p>\n<p>队列需要实现的基本方法有：<strong>添加和移除元素、获取队列中的元素个数、判断队列是否为空</strong>。使用python中的列表来实现队列：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">class Queue(object):\n    def __init__(self):\n        self._items &#x3D; []\n    \n    # 向队列尾部添加元素\n    def put(self, item):\n        self._items.append(item)\n    \n    # 从队列头部取出元素\n    def get(self):\n        return self._items.pop(0)\n    \n    # 获取队列中元素个数\n    def size(self):\n        return len(self._items)\n    \n    # 判断队列是否为空\n    def empty(self):\n        return self._items &#x3D;&#x3D; []\n    \n    def __repr__(self):\n        return f&#39;Queue(&#123;self._items&#125;)&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<p>但是，将Python的列表作为队列是不合适的，因为使用列表每次移除头部的元素都会使列表中所有元素向前移动一次，时间复杂度为O(n)。</p>\n<p>好在Python提供了专门的队列供我们使用：<code>queue.Queue</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">from queue import Queue\n\nif __name__ &#x3D;&#x3D; &quot;__main__&quot;:\n    queue &#x3D; Queue()\n    queue.put(&quot;hello&quot;)\n    print(&quot;添加一个元素后的大小:&quot;,queue.qsize())\n    queue.put(123)\n    print(&quot;添加一个元素后的大小:&quot;,queue.qsize())\n    print(&quot;移除的元素:&quot;,queue.get())\n    print(&quot;移除一个元素后的大小:&quot;,queue.qsize())\n    print(&quot;移除的元素:&quot;,queue.get())</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>实际上，更常用的队列的解决方案是使用下面的双端队列：<code>collections.deque</code>。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"栈\"><a href=\"#栈\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"栈\"></a>栈</h1><p>栈的基本思想是先进后出（FILO&#x2F;LIFO）。其中添加操作和移除操作都发生在顶端，另一端称为底端。</p>\n<p>由于先进后出具有反转的特性，所以它也有很多应用场景。如浏览器将url保存在栈中，访问一个网页就将对应url入栈，回退就将最顶部的url出栈。</p>\n<p>栈需要实现的基本方法有：<strong>添加和移除元素、获取队列中的元素个数、判断队列是否为空</strong>。使用python中的列表来实现栈：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">class Stack(object):\n    def __init__(self):\n        self._items &#x3D; []\n    \n    # 入栈\n    def put(self, item):\n        self._items.append(item)\n    \n    # 出栈\n    def get(self):\n        return self._items.pop(-1)\n    \n    # 获取栈中元素个数\n    def size(self):\n        return len(self._items)\n    \n    # 判断栈是否为空\n    def empty(self):\n        return self._items &#x3D;&#x3D; []\n    \n    def __repr__(self):\n        return f&#39;Stack(&#123;self._items&#125;)&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<p>因为栈的添加和移除都发生在栈尾，所以使用Python自带的列表实现栈的上述操作还是很高效的，时间复杂度都是O(1)。一般也是直接这样使用。</p>\n<p>另外，python也提供了符合栈语义的数据结构：<code>queue.LifoQueue</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">from queue import LifoQueue\n    \nif __name__ &#x3D;&#x3D; &quot;__main__&quot;:\n    stack &#x3D; LifoQueue()\n    stack.put(&quot;hello&quot;)\n    print(&quot;添加一个元素后的大小:&quot;,stack.qsize())\n    stack.put(123)\n    print(&quot;添加一个元素后的大小:&quot;,stack.qsize())\n    print(&quot;移除的元素:&quot;,stack.get())\n    print(&quot;移除一个元素后的大小:&quot;,stack.qsize())\n    print(&quot;移除的元素:&quot;,stack.get())</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>实际上，更常用的队列的解决方案是使用双端队列：<code>collection.deque</code>。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"双端队列\"><a href=\"#双端队列\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"双端队列\"></a>双端队列</h1><p>双端队列分前端（front）和后端（rear），两端都可以添加和移除元素。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>双端队列的英文名 deque（与 deck 同音）。</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/python/DSA/1/image-20221219190056118.png\" alt=\"image-20221219190056118\"></p>\n<p>在普通队列的基础上，双端队列还要求在队列的最左边以O(1)的时间复杂度添加和移除元素。所以它可以向下实现栈和队列。</p>\n<p>先使用python的列表来模拟双端队列的操作：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">class Deque(object):\n    def __init__(self):\n        self._items &#x3D; []\n    \n    def append(self, item):\n        self._items.append(item)\n    \n    def appendleft(self, item):\n        self._items.insert(0, item)\n    \n    def pop(self):\n        return self._items.pop()\n    \n    def popleft(self):\n        return self._items.pop(0)\n    \n    def size(self):\n        return len(self._items)\n    \n    def empty(self):\n        return self._items &#x3D;&#x3D; []\n    \n    def __repr__(self):\n        return f&#39;Deque(&#123;self._items&#125;)&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<p>显然，在列表最左边的操作是低效的。如果要保证两端的操作时间复杂度都是O(1)，需要用到链表（就不实现了)。</p>\n<p>使用<code>collections.deque</code>可以很好地完成双端队列的任务：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">from collections import deque\n    \nif __name__ &#x3D;&#x3D; &quot;__main__&quot;:\n    deq &#x3D; deque()\n    # 分别向右边和左边添加元素\n    deq.append(123)\n    deq.appendleft(456)\n    print(deq)\n    \n    # 支持迭代和下标访问，以及len()获取元素个数\n    for i in deq:\n        print(i)\n    print(deq[1])\n    print(len(deq))\n    \n    # 支持在中间插入元素\n    deq.insert(1, 789)\n    print(deq)\n    \n    # 支持按值查位置和元素计数\n    print(deq.index(789))\n    print(deq.count(123))\n    \n    # 分别从右边和左边移除元素\n    print(deq.pop())\n    print(deq)\n    print(deq.popleft())</code></pre>\n\n<p>可以看到，<code>collections.deque</code>既实现了在左边和右边增删元素，又提供了大多数python列表支持的方法。使得双端队列比Python自带的列表要高效得多，同时又不是太死板（对操作约束太严格）。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>也常常使用双端队列来实现栈和队列。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"链表\"><a href=\"#链表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"链表\"></a>链表</h1><p>Python并没有提供链表，所以需要我们自己实现。</p>\n<p>链表的结构如下，包含一个头指针和一串节点（也可以不使用头指针）。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/python/DSA/1/image-20221219203337577.png\" alt=\"image-20221219203337577\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>在C语言中，链表的实现需要用到指针。但是Python中并没有指针一说，该怎么实现链表呢？</p></blockquote>\n<p>实际上，Python中值传递传的就是地址，即将一个变量赋值给另一个变量后，两个变量都会指向同一个内存地址：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/python/DSA/1/image-20221219203810796.png\" alt=\"image-20221219203810796\"></p>\n<p>所以直接赋值就行了，不需要像C那样一会取地址，一会取值，凡色特了。</p>\n<p>链表的基本操作有：向头部插入元素、删除位置i处的节点、查找结点的位置等。使用Python实现链表：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">class LinkList(object):\n    class _Node(object):\n        def __init__(self, d, n&#x3D;None):\n            self.data &#x3D; d\n            self.next &#x3D; n  # 应该为_Node类型\n    \n    def __init__(self):\n        self.head &#x3D; None\n    \n    # 头插法\n    def add(self, data):\n        temp &#x3D; None\n        if self.head is not None:\n            temp &#x3D; LinkList._Node(data, self.head)\n        else: temp &#x3D; LinkList._Node(data, None)\n        self.head &#x3D; temp\n    \n    # 删除位置i处的节点\n    def remove(self, i):\n        index &#x3D; 0\n        if self.head is None: \n            print(&quot;This link list is None.&quot;);return -1\n        temp &#x3D; self.head\n        while index &lt; i-1:\n            temp &#x3D; temp.next;index +&#x3D; 1\n            if temp.next is None:\n                print(&quot;Index out of range.&quot;);return -1\n        if i &#x3D;&#x3D; 0: self.head &#x3D; temp.next\n        else: temp.next &#x3D; temp.next.next\n        return 0\n    \n    # 按值查找位置，返回列表\n    def search(self, v):\n        temp &#x3D; self.head\n        index &#x3D; 0;result &#x3D; []\n        while temp is not None:\n            if temp.data &#x3D;&#x3D; v:\n                result.append(index)\n            index +&#x3D; 1\n            temp &#x3D; temp.next\n        return result\n    \n    # 打印链表\n    def show(self):\n        temp &#x3D; self.head\n        print(&quot;head&quot;, end&#x3D;&#39;-&gt;&#39;)\n        while temp is not None:\n            print(temp.data, end&#x3D;&#39;-&gt;&#39;)\n            temp &#x3D; temp.next\n        print(&quot;None&quot;)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/python/DSA/1/image-20221219204247071.png\" alt=\"image-20221219204247071\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"练习\"><a href=\"#练习\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"练习\"></a>练习</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>检查HTML的标签是否闭合（假设仅出现需要闭合的标签）。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/python/DSA/1/image-20221219204542988.png\" alt=\"image-20221219204542988\"></p></blockquote>\n<p>使用栈来实现即可。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">from collections import deque\n\ndef solve(html: str):\n    i &#x3D; 0\n    stack &#x3D; deque()\n    while i &lt; len(html):\n        if html[i] !&#x3D; &quot;&lt;&quot;: i +&#x3D; 1;continue\n        j &#x3D; i + 1;flag &#x3D; 0\n        if html[j] &#x3D;&#x3D; &#39;&#x2F;&#39;: flag &#x3D; 1\n        while html[j] !&#x3D; &quot;&gt;&quot;: j +&#x3D; 1\n        if flag &#x3D;&#x3D; 0: stack.append(html[i+1:j])\n        elif stack[-1] &#x3D;&#x3D; html[i+2:j]: stack.pop()\n        else: return False\n        i &#x3D; j + 1\n    return True\n        \nif __name__ &#x3D;&#x3D; &quot;__main__&quot;:\n    s &#x3D; &quot;&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;title&gt;Example&lt;&#x2F;title&gt;&lt;&#x2F;head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Hello, world&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;&lt;&#x2F;body&gt;&lt;&#x2F;html&gt;&quot;\n    print(solve(s))</code></pre>\n\n","text":" 本篇的目标是使用Python实现常用的线性数据结构并使用，包括：栈、队列、双端队列、链表等。 队列队列的的排序原则是先进先出（FIFO）。其中添加操作发生在队列的尾部，移除操作发生在队列的头部。 先进先出的使用是很普遍的，如生活中的排队，操作系统中的阻塞队列、就绪队列，网络中的...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6.5k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"专业课内","slug":"专业课内","count":29,"path":"api/categories/专业课内.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构与算法","slug":"数据结构与算法","count":4,"path":"api/tags/数据结构与算法.json"},{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count